room_title: Escape room "The List" by Chico Escape Rooms in Chico
room_address: 55 Declaration Dr Suite C Chico, CA 95973
room_description: You have just been informed that your name did not make it onto the nice list.  Not knowing what else to do, you come up with a plan.  You bribe that head elf to secretly let you into Santa's office where the "nice list" is cleverly hidden.  While Santa is away for a short time, you will be granted access.  You must find the list and add your name to it before Santa returns!
